### Notification Management Endpoints

### Get User Notifications
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/notifications?limit=50&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Send Notification
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "id": "notif-123",
  "user_id": "user-123",
  "title": "Order Update",
  "body": "Your order has been confirmed!",
  "type": "order",
  "data": "{\"order_id\": \"order-123\"}"
}

###

### Mark Notification as Read
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications/notif-123/read
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Delete Notification
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications/notif-123
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get Notifications Stream (Not Implemented - WebSocket)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/notifications/stream
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Send Push Notification (Not Implemented - FCM)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/push-notifications/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "user_id": "user-123",
  "title": "New Promotion!",
  "body": "Get 20% off your next order",
  "data": {
    "promotion_id": "promo-123",
    "discount": "20%"
  }
}

